Class Card

java.lang.Object
  comp125.Card

public class Card
extends java.lang.Object

Card encodes a playing card that contains a suit and rank. suit can be an integer from 1 to 4 Suits - 1 representing clubs, 2 representing diamonds, 3 representing hearts, 4 representing spades Rank - 1 representing Ace 2 to 10 representing their numerical valued card 11 representing jack 12 representing queen 13 representing king
